rComments: He is the most caring prof I have met in my entire undergraduate career. He truly cares for his students and wants you to do well. His lectures were very insightful and his office hours are extremely helpful. He is a lot of background in his field and is willing to help with career advice. Would love to take another course with him! :)
Perhaps what is most mentionable about him is that he's a very sweet and kind hearted person: he talks to people with a lot of empathy and respect and is always there to extend a helping hand needed.
